{"tid":347894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★未整好就cut  港鐵接駁巴士下午4時15分停止服務","createTime":"2017-08-05T08:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T13:35:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0dfb9369abc1c578e5d061760d346332f0737a9","tid":347894,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1346523_1_20170805162527.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1346523_1_20170805162527.jpg&d=RteHjx9wNTTgmW3pMpHAc8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=47c9b7b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1346523_1_20170805162527.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1346523-20170805.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1346523-20170805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RteHjx9wNTTgmW3pMpHAc8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=bd4b813d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1346523-20170805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dccb02ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1346523-20170805.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n2017-08-05 HKT 16:15<br />\n港鐵觀塘站附近有訊號故障，觀塘綫列車服務受阻。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，目前觀塘綫來往黃埔站及調景嶺站的列車服務，調整為5分鐘一班車；而來往彩虹站和油塘站的免費接駁巴士運作至下午4時15分就會停止服務。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵又說，觀塘綫列車駛經牛頭角站和藍田站路段時需要慢駛，觀塘綫來往黃埔站及調景嶺站的行車時間預計需要額外5至10分鐘。"},{"pid":"40ad4baae330e40c4689253c52c606515af64b4d","tid":347894,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1346523_1_20170805162527.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1346523_1_20170805162527.jpg&h=2f4d8aa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"615f422b79cb7bb4bbfa9ad9eda9ccf79f702